      "step_order": 1,
      "step_title": "Overview",
      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">This guide shows you how to access and read your &#39;Shift Report&#39; in the QPOS BackOffice. The &#39;Shift Report&#39; provides a detailed summary of all activities that occurred between a POS register&#39;s opening and closing times, including sales, payment breakdowns, discounts, and cash drawer movements. Understanding this report is crucial for daily reconciliation and monitoring cashier performance.</span></p>",
