      "step_order": 2,
      "step_title": "Before You Begin",
      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Access to your QPOS BackOffice.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">A stable internet connection.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Cashiers must properly &#39;Open Shift&#39; and &#39;Close Shift&#39; on the POS device for accurate reporting.</span></li></ul>",
